feedback: Looking good!  Interested in seeing what the survey will tell.
For dietary restrictions and allergy sections I would consider moving the none option to the bottom so it is easier to find

“Please give each topic a rating from 1 (least important) to 5 (most important).” I found this statement to be a bit misleading, as it almost implied that I could only pick one of the options to be most important - but I understood the general gist. Also, entering my phone number as xxxxxxxxxx should work instead of only as xxx-xxx-xxxx.
Seems pretty straightforward! Could zoom out a little to week view not just day.
